Simple as 1-2-3

How PopFlyPal Works

1
🤾

Throw It Up

Toss PopFlyPal into the air just like a real baseball. It feels natural in your hand and launches beautifully.

2
🪂

Watch It Float

The built-in parachute deploys instantly, slowing the descent so kids have plenty of time to track the ball.

3
🥳

Make the Catch!

Kids position themselves and catch it — building real muscle memory and confidence with every rep.

4
📈

Level Up

The carabiner clip lets you swap to a smaller parachute as skills improve — true gradual progression built right in.
